WEBVTT

00:00:59.240 --> 00:01:00.456
No pressure.

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:02.000
(Laughter)

00:01:03.040 --> 00:01:05.616
From mythology to science fiction,

00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:08.376
human versus machine

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:11.160
has been often portrayed
as a matter of life and death.

00:01:11.960 --> 00:01:13.536
John Henry,

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:15.256
called the steel-driving man

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:19.056
in the 19th century
African American folk legend,

00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:20.456
was pitted in a race

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:23.216
against a steam-powered hammer

00:01:23.240 --> 00:01:25.600
bashing a tunnel through mountain rock.

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:31.000
John Henry's legend
is a part of a long historical narrative